### Exchangeratesapi.io API Tests (Requires API key)
### See pricing: https://exchangeratesapi.io/#pricing_plan

# API key is loaded from .env file
@apiKey = {{$dotenv EXCHANGERATESAPI_KEY}}

### Get latest rates with USD base
GET https://api.exchangeratesapi.io/v1/latest?access_key={{apiKey}}&base=USD&symbols=GBP,EUR

###

### Get historical rates for specific date (requires starter plan)
GET https://api.exchangeratesapi.io/v1/2024-01-01?access_key={{apiKey}}&base=USD&symbols=GBP,EUR

###

### Get time series data (requires professional plan)
GET https://api.exchangeratesapi.io/v1/timeseries?access_key={{apiKey}}&start_date=2024-01-01&end_date=2024-01-31&base=USD&symbols=GBP,EUR

###

### Convert specific amount (requires starter plan)
GET https://api.exchangeratesapi.io/v1/convert?access_key={{apiKey}}&from=USD&to=GBP&amount=100

###

### Get all supported symbols
GET https://api.exchangeratesapi.io/v1/symbols?access_key={{apiKey}}
